-The great facts that Newton
discovered have now become
the property of the [underline]public[/underline],
& though all the labour
which this great Man
employed has not [underline]fortunately[/underline]
fallen to the lot of all
yet the benefit is [underline]immense[/underline][underline],,[/underline]
– What [underline]a picture[/underline] does this
[underline]man offer to us[/underline], how
beautiful how grand untouched
[underline]by Ambition[/underline], He gave up

his days to the discovery of
[underline]truth.[/underline] [deletion]That [/deletion]We are
delighted with the thoughts
of the [underline]Academy of Athens[/underline]

